author: Asha Prakash
title: Anna Katherina releases single
text:
Singer Anna Katherina, who shot to fame with the wacky Appangalembadum, released her first single, titled Honeybee.
The album has been described as a musical story teller and talks about the innocence of childhood. The singer is pregnant with her second baby but decided to go ahead with the relaase. "Honey bee is a simple jazz malayalam song...Though I am 7.8 months pregnant, my music lovers still went ahead n accepted me with both arms wide open smile," she wrote on her page. The singer recently composed the title song of Kavya Madhavan starrer Akashavani .
